data.description: Absolutely Gorgeous and close to Majors Golf Course and shopping! All upgraded, 18'' tile, high ceilings and blinds. Beautiful kitchen cabinets, stainless steel appliances, granite counters w/backsplash, breakfast bar and large hall pantry. Nice Breakfast nook open to large family room w/sliders to   patio. Formal dining room w/fantastic trey ceiling and chandelier. Light bright formal living room w/view to patio. Stunning Master suite w/engineered wood floor, trey ceiling, french doors to patio, his/her closets, double sinks w/granite counters, garden tub, separate shower, and enclosed toilet. Good size extra bedrooms w/carpet and ceiling fans and beautiful second bathroom with tile floors and granite counter. Oversized screened patio w/view to beautifully landscaped yard. Water heater and a/c two years
data.whatILove: Great curb appeal. Granite in kitchen & baths. Separate laundry room. Huge lanai with gorgeous pool all screened. Interior designer colors and beautifully decorated.
